## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on a limited selection of sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was constrained by the availability of online resources and the scope of the query. Additionally, the interpretations of philosophical motivations for seeking knowledge can be subjective and vary widely among individuals. Further research could include a broader range of cultural and historical perspectives to provide a more comprehensive understanding.